task.summary:
Implemented share feature of a thing Implemented barcode scanner to add barcodes Added exit dialog Fixed bug where app would crash if back is pressed on landscape mode
Cleaned up code
Fixed bug where barcode was not stored fixed bug that caused crash when in Thing detail view

-Implemented barcode lookup feature. Scanned item information will be fetched from www.outpan.com and will automatically be added to your things. This feature is accessed from the main page
-removed barcode scanning in thing page as it was deemed unnecessary
-Implemented networking feature and attached it to dependency injection -Implemented networking availability checks -Bugfixes -Cleaned up structure and code
Fixed bug where existing barcode is not displayed in detailed thing page. Fixed bug where use made changes was not retained when rotating screen in detailed thing page.

Implemented SearchView in list page Implemented Search functionality Implemented Search while typing Implemented Search based on what or where Implemented Sort functionality based on Where, What and Date Fixed Menu bug where menu items got duplicated Tweak stability of app Minor bug fixes Cleaned up code
Removed lookup button from main page as it is deprecated. Fixed bug where app would crash when searching in landscape mode
Fixed tests and added class for new tests
Fixed Format of date in thing Fixed Sorting (Implemented SelectionSort instead) MergeSort was implemented wrong.
Fixed sort error Added tests for search and sort
-Cleaned up code for final release -Added documentation -Added report for final handin
